<plot>Ex-soldier Ralph Phillips, leaving his army camp, is ecstatic at being a civilian again, but finds that all his friends have started to raise families and that there is no place for him in his home town. Dejected, Ralph considers re-enlisting, and he's visited by two opposing figures, one advocating civilian life, the other arguing in favor of the military. The latter convinces Ralph to run back to the army camp.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?007114</url></doc>
